<li><a href="http://www.daat.ac.il/daat/kitveyet/sinay/hazohar-2.htm|" class="external text" title="http://www.daat.ac.il/daat/kitveyet/sinay/hazohar-2.htm|" rel="nofollow">Menachem Kasher's article on authenticity of the Zohar</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.digital-brilliance.com/kab/karr/zie.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.digital-brilliance.com/kab/karr/zie.pdf" rel="nofollow">Notes on the Zohar in English</a></li>
</ul>


